    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "A shortcut’s ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "key",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " that is defined on an US-English keyboard",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "layout might not be reachable on international layouts.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "For example the shortcut ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "⌘[",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " works well for the US layout but is",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "hard to reach for German users.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "On the German keyboard layout, pressing ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "⌥5",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " will produce",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "[",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ", which causes the shortcut to become ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "⌥⌘5",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "If configured, which is the default behavior, automatic shortcut",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "remapping will convert it to ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "⌘Ö",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "In addition to that, some keyboard shortcuts carry information",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "about directionality.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "Right-aligning a block of text or seeking forward in context of music",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "playback are such examples. These kinds of shortcuts benefit from the option",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.SwiftUI/documentation/SwiftUI/KeyboardShortcut/Localization-swift.struct/withoutMirroring",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "to tell the system that they won’t be flipped when running in a",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "right-to-left context.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
